-- Finmeccanica’s Pansa to Run Operating Units, Cutillo Named CFO
-- B y   A n d r e w   D a v i s
-- 2012-05-16T20:06:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-16/finmeccanica-s-pansa-to-run-operating-units-cutillo-named-cfo.html
Finmeccanica SpA (FNC)  said that Chief
Operating Officer Alessandro Pansa will take on management of
the defense contractor’s operating units and named Gian Piero
Cutillo to take on Orsi’s role as chief financial officer.  Giuseppe Orsi remains chief executive officer with
responsibility for strategy, personnel, external communications
adn business development, Finmeccanica said in an e-mailed
statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andrew Davis in Rome at 
 abdavis@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
